File: (eNCA\Screenshot) BRAKPAN - A Grade 10 pupil at Geluksdal Secondary School in Brakpan has been stabbed to death after a fight at school. WATCH: Education in Crisis | Brakpan Matric pupil killed in electrocution It's alleged the stabbing occurred after a group of boys pepper-sprayed some pupils. A confrontation then erupted when another group tried to reprimand them. Gauteng Education spokesperson, Steve Mabona says that the perpetrator is not a learner of the school. Mabona said, "the perpetrator we understand, has been taken to hospital."